---
description: "Intent CLI workflow helper"
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: false
---

Use Intent CLI when a repository already uses `.intent/` or when the user asks
to maintain semantic history with `itt`.

- Read `itt inspect --json` before substantive work.
- Continue the active intent when it matches the task.
- Use `itt run start`, `itt snap`, `itt adopt`, and `itt decide` only for meaningful steps.
- Re-read `itt inspect --json` after state changes instead of guessing.
